WEBVTT

00:03:29.038 --> 00:03:30.788
i stvaraju savršene uslove

00:03:30.788 --> 00:03:33.246
za rast kalcijum karbonata.

00:03:33.246 --> 00:03:35.329
Ovi kristali polako popunjavaju pukotine,

00:03:35.329 --> 00:03:36.829
i, otprilke, nakon tri sedmice,

00:03:36.829 --> 00:03:38.204
vrijedni mikrobi

00:03:38.204 --> 00:03:39.913
mogu potpuno da poprave pukotine

00:03:39.913 --> 00:03:42.704
širine do gotovo jednog milimetra.

00:03:42.704 --> 00:03:43.871
Kada se pukotine popune,

00:03:43.871 --> 00:03:46.038
bakterije i gljive prave spore

00:03:46.038 --> 00:03:47.579
i onda pređu u uspavano stanje -

00:03:47.579 --> 00:03:49.829
spremne da započnu novi ciklus oporavka

00:03:49.829 --> 00:03:51.288
kada se pukotine opet pojave.

00:03:51.704 --> 00:03:54.246
Iako je ova tehnika
dugo vremena izučavana,

00:03:54.329 --> 00:03:56.829
pred nama je dug put
prije nego što se uvede

00:03:56.871 --> 00:03:58.913
u svjetsku proizvodnju betona.

00:03:58.954 --> 00:04:01.496
Ali ove spore imaju ogroman potencijal